comments: Oladipo (HOU) makes marginal contact to Bridges' (PHX) arm during his driving shot attempt. The contact does not affect Bridges' ability to defend.
Tate (HOU) briefly places his arm around Ayton's (PHX) front and he immediately slides it off. The contact is marginal.
Nwaba (HOU) makes marginal contact with Paul's (PHX) shoulder on the perimeter.
Nwaba (HOU) jumps towards Paul (PHX) and stops short, establishing himself in a legal guarding position as Paul seeks out contact during his jump shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) places his hands against Wood's (HOU) back during the rebound, but he does not extend into him and the contact is marginal.
Oladipo (HOU) makes contact to Ayton's (PHX) arm that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Oladipo (HOU) makes leg to leg contact to Booker (PHX) during the drive that affects his SQBR.
Ayton (PHX) turns his body and makes contact to Oladipo's (HOU) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Nwaba (HOU) reaches in and makes marginal contact with Booker (PHX) before he begins his drive to the basket.
Nwaba (HOU) makes marginal contact to Booker's (PHX) body that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
